headline: 3 Red-Hot Growth Stocks to Buy in 2025
summary: Picking up the latest hot growth stock can be smart, but only if it's at the right price.  After Nvidia's (NASDAQ: NVDA) latest sell-off, it's more than 10% down from its 2024 highs, making it an interesting stock to catch on sale.  Nvidia's growth has been unbelievable, as its latest quarter saw its revenue rise by 94% year over year.
